Italy May Block Groupama’s Fondiaria Stake Purchase, MF Says

-- B y   A r m o r e l   K e n n a
-- 
2011-02-22T07:50:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-22/italy-may-block-groupama-s-fondiaria-stake-purchase-mf-says.html
Italy’s stock-market regulator may
not authorize Groupama SA’s purchase of a stake in  Fondiaria-Sai
SpA , while approving its acquisition of a share of the holding
company that controls the insurer, newspaper MF reported.  Consob, the regulator, is likely to communicate its
decision by Feb. 25, according to the Italian newspaper.  Groupama said Jan. 13 it would consider acquiring a stake
of as much as 20 percent in Fondiaria-Sai.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Armorel Kenna in Milan at 
 akenna@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at 
 cperri@bloomberg.net  